Package: PhosR
Type: Package
Title: A set of methods and tools for comprehensive analysis of phosphoproteomics data
Version: 0.1.5
Author: Pengyi Yang, Taiyun Kim, Hani Kim
Maintainer: Taiyun Kim <taiyun.kim91@gmail.com>
Description: PhosR is a package for the comprenhensive analysis of phosphoproteomic data. There are two major components to PhosR: processing and downstream analysis. 
